           MOVE CLIS-TIPO TO WS-CLIS-TIPO-ANT
           MOVE 1 TO WS-TOTAL-CLIS-TIPO
           MOVE 42 TO WS-CUENTA-LINEA

           IF WS-FIN-CLI
              NEXT SENTENCE
           ELSE                                                         00421000
